Text:
There is always something new to know about from Mr. Davis books. 
Thank you very much.

First of all, Thank you for uploading so many great audiobooks. You are probably my #1 source for listening material.
This upload is missing some parts. 
From part 104 (just starting Franklin Pierce) it jumps in part 105 to Lincoln milestones.
So it's missing the rest of Franklin Pierce, all of James Buchanan and pretty well all of Lincoln's presidency.
Any way these can be found and put up as a extra torrent?
Many thanks again.
Fyremonkey - Nope. This a rip from a library CD. EAC tested, so if something is wrong, it's wrong with the physical CDs. They only have the one copy.
